overview: On December 4th GCW is coming with second event in a row - it's One Afternoon Only live on FITE+ straight from The Arena in Jeffersonville, IN. First matches of the lineup are already announced and you can check them below:  Nick Wayne vs Starboy Charlie Effy vs Cole Radrick  Tony Deppen vs Billy Starkz Los Macizos and Jimmy Lloyd vs The Rejects and Mad Man Pondo  Jordan Olive vs 1 Called Manders Axton Ray vs AJ Gray Jack Cartwheel vs Shane Mercer
title: GCW One Afternoon Only
